abce.util.io
Class FileManager

java.lang.Object
  abce.util.io.FileManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class FileManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The file manager is an object that keeps track of registered controllers (e.g. simulation objects) and files registered (but not checked to be guaranteed) by those controllers. When the last controller unregisters from the file manager, all registered files are closed.
